Difference of Studying MBBS in Ukraine Vs Philippines for Indian Students

  • Differentiate between Universities
  • Cost of Education
  • Advantage for Indian Students
  • Cost of Living
  • PG in Philippines vs Ukraine
  • Scope After MBBS in Philippines or Ukraine
  • Studying MBBS in Philippines or Ukraine is Worth it or Not
  • Conclusion

Every year, thousands of Indian students take admission in abroad to pursue MBBS. Various countries provide high-quality medical education at very affordable fees. The process of admission in MBBS in medical universities abroad is very simple & hassle-free. Even, there is no need to qualify any entrance exam.

Abroad medical universities provide world-class infrastructure with all the latest equipment. Indian students that wish to study MBBS in Philippines or MBBS in Ukraine can take a look at the detailed analysis of studying MBBS in both the countries and choose for themselves the most viable option.

{/* */}

Differentiate between Universities

MBBS in Philippines medical universities

The Philippines is one of the best destinations for Indian students to study MBBS. Every year, more than 9000 students take admission to study MBBS in Philippines. Philippines medical universities are recognized by the MCI & WHO. The top MCI & WHO approved Philippines medical universities follow the US education system. The medicinal course provided to students in the Philippines is known as the MD program (Doctor of Medicine).

Philippines medical colleges offer a low tuition fee structure for Indian students with a high quality of education. After successfully completing the MBBS, the students from the Philippines get opportunities to work in power nation countries. The medium of instruction in Philippines medical colleges/universities is English.

MBBS in Ukraine medical universities

Most of the students take admission in Ukraine to study MBBS because it comprises of several top-class Government medical universities that provide MBBS at a very affordable fee. After completing the MBBS in Ukraine, the students can have lots of career opportunities in various countries.

There is no requirement to give any entrance test to take admission in Ukraine Medical University. All the Ukraine medical universities are recognized by the MCI, WHO, and UNESCO. The medical degree obtained from Ukraine medical university is globally accepted and has reasonable tuition fee and a top-class education system.

Cost of Education

The cost of education of MBBS in Philippines vs Ukraine is as follows:

Country Fee structure per year
Philippines 12 lakhs to 15 lakhs
Ukraine 20 lakhs to 25 lakhs

Advantage for Indian Students

Advantages for Indian students to study MBBS in Philippines:

  • A medical program provided by the Philippines to their students is recognized worldwide.
  • English is spoken in the Philippines so there would not be any problem while interacting with others. The language of coaching is also English.
  • MCI (Medical Council of India) approves medical colleges as well as universities and follows the US education system.
  • The students who have passed MBBS from the Philippines can also practice in India.
  • A unified problem-based learning approach offers better exposure to future medical practitioners.
  • Advanced teaching techniques with outstanding facilities equipped with the well-established infrastructure
  • The students can also have the option to start working on preparation for the United States Medical Licensing Examination (USMLE) to study Post Graduate Degrees.
  • The Philippines is extremely safe for Indian students and the environment is also safe.
  • There is no donation or capitation fee required in these universities.
  • Philippines MBBS College provides the best education at affordable rates.
  • The cost of living is quite favorable for Indian students as there are excellent boarding and lodging provided by the university with the availability of Indian food for the students.

Advantages for Indian students to study MBBS in Ukraine

  • All Ukraine medical universities are managed by the Ministry of Education and Science of Ukraine and offer high-quality medical education to students.
  • The students do not need to pay any donation or capitation fee to take admission in Ukraine medical college.
  • Ukraine medical college encourages the students to take part in several seminars and international conferences, and other scientific projects in several international universities.
  • Ukraine medical universities have accreditation from WHO, UNESCO, MCI and medical councils of many other counties.
  • The students are taught in English for MBBS course which enables the international students to adapt to the environment quickly.
  • The cost of living in Ukraine for students is also affordable as compared to other countries.
  • After competing MBBS from Ukraine Medical University, Indian students can easily get a job in any country because the MBBS degree acquired from a Ukraine University is recognized by the MCI.
Cost of Living
Country Cost of living per month
Philippines $ 180-200
Ukraine $ 150-250

Cost of living in Philippines

The cost of living is very low that assist the Indian students to afford the expenses easily which is around $ 180-200 per month. Philippines medical universities provide great accommodation facilities in top Philippines colleges to medical students. The students can stay in University hostels at very reasonable fees. The hostels are furnished with furniture. The students can pay the cost of hostel along with the MBBS fees.

Cost of living in Ukraine

Ukraine is one of the beautiful places that provide study environment to the students to do excel in their studies. The cost of living in Ukraine is affordable with a healthy environment as compared to many other countries. The cost of living is around $ 150-250 per month. Ukraine medical universities provide wonderful accommodation facilities such as hostels for Indian students that provide all the essential facilities and amenities with Indian food, and many more.

PG in Philippines vs Ukraine

Following are the PG options after completing MBBS in Philippines:

  • Philippines universities provide several PG courses
  • The students can choose to pursue courses in several disciplines
  • They only need to fetch documents relating to their graduation to take admission in PG courses.

Following are the PG options after completing MBBS in Ukraine:

  • The students can do PG course in India or in any country of their choice after completing MBBS in Ukraine.
  • They can become a surgeon or anything else as per their study field in any country because the MBBS degree from top Ukraine universities has worldwide recognition.
  • If students want to pursue PG in any country, they need to clear the respective entrance exam or screening test of that country.
Scope After MBBS in Philippines or Ukraine

Scope after MBBS in Philippines

  • The students can take admission in masters in Medicine
  • Once they complete MBBS in Ukraine and after qualify MCI screening test can do medicine practice in India.
  • The student that graduate from the Philippines universities have bright career options
  • They can choose to migrate to USA and UK for further study
  • They can also choose to go back to India and practice medicine
  • They can practice medicine in India after qualifying MCI screening tests
  • They can study PG courses in Philippines Universities

Scope after MBBS in Ukraine

  • The students can opt for masters in Medicine after completing MBBS in Ukraine
  • After qualifying MCI screening test, they can do their practice in India.
  • They can do a job in any hospital of any country because the MBBS degree obtained from Ukraine medical colleges is valid in every country.
Studying MBBS in Philippines or Ukraine is Worth it or Not

MBBS in Philippines is the best considerable destination to study a course of medicine for Indian students. It enables the students to have brighter career growth after study MBBS in Philippines. It provides the magnificent theoretical as well as practical education which empowers the candidates to become successful practitioners. Medical Degrees get from Philippines Medical Colleges or Universities have worldwide recognition. After completion of MBBS in Philippines, the students can opt for PG in another country or practice as a Doctor in India as well as in another foreign country after clear the National Exit Exam.

Ukraine is one of great destinations for the students who wish to study MBBS in abroad. It consists of various top-class Ukraine medical college/universities that offer MBBS course at a very low-budget. The top Ukraine medical universities taught MBBS in Ukraine in English and provide high-quality education as well as top-class infrastructure to the students.

Conclusion

We have provided detailed information regarding MBBS in Philippines and MBBS in Ukraine. The students can choose any country as per their interest and budget Philippines and Ukraine both provide high-quality education at reasonable fees. After completing MBBS in Philippines and MBBS in Ukraine, the students can have lots of career opportunities.
